recordedBy: Andrew Salywon; Neil Snow & Martin de la Crus
locality: Paraje la isla, en la carretera a Guzmancito el Albinal. En la zone innundada, vegetacion costera.
occurrenceRemarks: Shrub 4 m high, growing on embankment 2 m above mud flat. Leaves very shiny green on both sides, chrushed leaves fragrant, somewhat rubbery, held vertically at midday. Fruits hard, green. Bark smoth gray; wood very hard.
name: Psidium dictyophyllum Urb. & Ekman

locality: Persque' ile Nord-Oeste: 5.5 Km al nordeste de Mole St. Nicolas en la carretera costera a Jean Rabel.
